column1: Daily Weather Observations for Kyabram, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3039.201603
Most observations from Kyabram, but evaporation from Tatura.
Tatura is about 21 km from Kyabram, and evaporation is included as a guide only.
Temperature, humidity, wind and rainfall observations are from Kyabram {station 080091}
Pressure observations are from Echuca Aerodrome {station 080015}
Evaporation observations are from Tatura Inst Sustainable Ag {station 081049}
